<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6647] Bad error message when missing resource from ZK when parsing Schema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6647</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Creating a collection via Collection API. Schema points to a file which is not in our config folder in ZooKeeper. Getting the infamous error message &lt;tt&gt;ZkSolrResourceLoader does not support getConfigDir()&lt;/tt&gt; instead of the more helpful message about which resource is missing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12750020">SOLR-6647</key>
            <summary>Bad error message when missing resource from ZK when parsing Schema</summary>
